cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks for building/floor classification and location estimation based on Wi-Fi fingerprinting. This involves techniques related to machine learning (cs.LG), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), and systems and control (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG, followed by cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.CV, and cs.SY.
